ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大埔出沙田行吐露港，<br />\n我跟p條例左線+行70就俾人砵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吐露港行70真係巴士都過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一係就推推推</blockquote><br />\n屌<br />\n咁d人見到P牌又行左線好心就自己過佢頭啦<br />\n<br />\n推乜撚野姐推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n掛緊P 吐露港行左線行70有時都俾巴士大貨車推<br />\n有D私家車仲閃你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以發夢果陣都唔會行70<br />\n不過好撚驚後面有個寶馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d564c2e0515ad3acc38a27b3ceb9551630d5410","tid":123690,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔好痴線啦<br />\n一個交通警撚有權逼你驗車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋,點解係15km,因為香港所有超速影相都係超過15km先影囉<br />\n唔係話寬鬆,只係大家都明儀器係有誤差,就算佢出告票,唔認罪好大機會告唔入<br />\n所以超過15km咁多就100%肯定你超速,抵俾人抄啦</blockquote><br />\n冇權驗?<br />\n咦 擋風玻璃啡啡地喎<br />\nbumper原廠架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拖返去驗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係咁,你架車原則上就要驗左車先落得地行嘅<br />\n如果佢無合理懷疑之下拖人架車去驗<br />\n驗完出嚟乜事都無嘅,你覺得佢自己會無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然,你本身改晒車就抵死嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,車速標係一樣絕對唔會準嘅儀器<br />\n計數方法係用車胎轉速嚟估算<br />\n但係實際行車嘅時候,路面情況,車胎新舊,好多呢d外在因素影響<br />\n咁司機如果收到嘅資訊唔正確,而導致輕微錯誤,例如超速,其實係法律上無犯法<br />\n所以唔係話佢支雷射槍準d,測到你超速,你就犯法嫁<br />\n<br />\n如果係可以咁抄嘅,所有高速入口出口整部相機,有車行過就影<br />\n有晒出入口時間,然後加埋公路長度計返平均車速<br />\n香港人渣車9成超速添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問你有冇車？</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實係條路限速+15內唔抄,安全起見個人就揸開+10嘅</blockquote><br />\n試下行吐路港入大埔100轉80位，90行去睇下影唔影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過90係無影嘅。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講緊邊個位？"},{"pid":"f8764c834b9f141d8ec1aedf8e032588b98771ef","tid":123690,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十年前可能15 都捉唔到<br />\n宜家科技咁先進<br />\n要捉超過10km 有幾難<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係捉唔捉到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係捉到,上庭唔認罪之後,佢證明唔到你架車當時顯示個車速係咪真係超速<br />\n結果疑點利益歸於被告,所以告唔入<br />\n但係超速超過15,就超過左器材誤差範圍,咁就肯定告得入</blockquote>靠害咩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲儀器全部有晒數據誤差有幾多<br />\n佢落簿個數係扣晒誤差既數<br />\n你上庭同個官講啲咁既野同申請交多幾倍罰款有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DowvM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DowvM3.jpg&h=ad2adf92&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係支槍個誤差吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁司機睇果個速度標係咪100%準吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個速度標就用車胎轉速同車胎一周長度換算嘅<br />\n咁車胎新舊,路面平滑程度,呢d係咪誤差吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩邊誤差加埋會係幾多吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,你拉返上去睇下,淨係呢個post都好幾個話條路+10唔抄<br />\n點解個個都話條路+10無事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為事實上+10真係唔抄囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講咁多做乜<br />\n下次超完試下咁樣同個官講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都話+10唔抄,又洗乜上庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超過15收信就俾錢啦,又係洗乜上庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算真係上庭,只需要講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「我唔知個警察影到d乜,我淨係知我個車速標就顯示住70嘅」</span><br />\n其他乜都唔洗解釋,因為舉證責任係控方到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我整壞架車個速度計係咪代表超幾多都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都話人地落簿係用佢減左誤差既儀器落簿<br />\n你係咁話自己速度計冇超做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年林建岳嘥幾百萬就係用儀器有誤差黎打先打得甩<br />\n自此之後全部落得簿都係扣晒誤差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解+10多數冇事？<br />\n因為唔扣分只罰錢<br />\n警察要捉鳩你只能話你真係樣衰咗<br />\n<br />\n過10就捉係因為開始扣到你分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cadb14e0aaa4043dd3da8b74668cdd9440cbfa5","tid":123690,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc